  "texts": [
    "None of the existing (external) boards seem to require full-time work.",
    "Members of Meta's Oversight Board work part-time [85].",
    "And members of Axon's AI and Policing Technologies Ethics Board only had two official board meetings per year, with ad-hoc contact between these meetings [18].The more time members spend working on the board, the more they can engage with individual cases.",
    "This would be crucial if cases are complex and stakes are high (e.g.",
    "if the board supports pre-deployment risk assessments)."
